title: Bunny Raven...or....How to Make a Titananimal Disappear
description: The Amazing Mumbo is up to his old tricks. And when the Titans try to stop the madcap, magician in mid-performance, Mumbo pulls a fast one. With a wave of his wand, he sucks the Titans into his hat, where our heroes discover a strange, magical world of weirdness. But in this world, Mumbo's holding all the cards. In a poof of magic, he changes the Titans into animals and takes away their powers. Can the Titanimals find their way out of the hat before Mubmo makes them disappear forever?
